node.text: Here’s the process💨 40ft long 🗿 6ft tall & around 15,000 pounds of stone! It’s crafted from dry stone and it took 2 months to build. It was my first time ever working with stone so it was a wild puzzle ✨ Stoked to build something new for my family so they can enjoy the backyard views 🙌🏼 #DIY #stonewalls #backyardproject #arch #architecture

node.text:
Today I get to celebrate getting to marry the love my life 🙌🏼 3 years! I remember right when you walked through that door. That 1st time seeing you, you were holding our baby deer 🐕 (yep creature & yes in that black leather jacket.) I’m so  lucky 💙 

To many more adventures with my best friend in this 🌎🙌🏼 @jillianbachinsky Like I said before if creatch wants in I want in forever!
